initialize() - Static method in class com.sdk.inplayer.configuration.InPlayer
Authenticates this client as belonging to your application. This must be called before your application can use the InPlayer SDK . The recommended way is to put a call to InPlayer.initialize in your Application's onCreate method: public class MyApplication extends Application { public void onCreate() { InPlayer.initialize(configuration); } }
